# Cursor IDE Rules for Hexagonal Architecture Refactoring

> **Purpose:** Specific AI coding guidelines for refactoring Phase 0 & Phase 1 to Hexagonal Architecture
> **Context:** Converting existing vendor-coupled code to vendor-agnostic abstraction layer
> **Priority:** These rules take precedence over .cursorrules during refactoring work

---

## 🎯 Refactoring Mission

You are refactoring an existing Golang fintech codebase from **vendor-coupled** to **vendor-agnostic Hexagonal Architecture**.

**DO NOT write new features. ONLY refactor existing code.**

