### Rule 3: Incremental Refactoring (One Service at a Time)

```
✅ CORRECT ORDER:
1. Create WalletService interface
2. Create FormanceWalletAdapter (wraps existing client)
3. Create InMemoryWalletAdapter (for tests)
4. Update ONE service to use interface
5. Verify tests pass
6. Commit
7. Move to NEXT service

❌ WRONG: Refactoring everything at once
```

**Branch Strategy:**
```bash
# One branch per refactoring task
git checkout -b refactor/R0.2.1-event-store-interface
# Complete task, test, commit
git checkout -b refactor/R0.2.2-event-horizon-adapter
# etc.
```

